-02-12T04:12:37.000Z","msg":"齋口唔齋心"},{"pid":"453cd3a6ef21e0785e3bfcd2fd501f47996874e2","tid":117062,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T07:02:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>倒如：素咕嚕肉，素鴨<br />\n簡直不知所謂</blockquote><br />\n呢D真係不如食肉<br />\n<br />\n齋口不齋心"},{"pid":"9ab8cce9ed44998b6e9558a74318d2393a8bcf9f","tid":117062,"uid":30892,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T07:07:00.000Z","msg":"肉你覺得好食有部分係來自個調味料<br />\n你覺得個調味料好食 又想唔食肉 咁咪食同樣調味方法既素食食材囉 關咩齋口唔齋心事<br />\n<br />\n利申齋叉燒同豬肉叉燒當兩種食物 兩隻都鍾意"},{"pid":"5d925cdb0a39f7302141eb9d3100f84f5b65f379","tid":117062,"uid":30892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T07:10:23.000Z","msg":"去美國去歐洲玩 啲餐廳有成頁無肉餐單 （就算冇一頁 都有幾個set係可以完整食一餐無肉而營養均衡）<br />\n香港大部份餐廳做唔到 而素食主義已經出現左咁多年 係香港既餐飲文化問題定素食者既問題？"},{"pid":"bc83a454d862246f329b8483c403af91d5e32cc7","tid":117062,"uid":57337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T12:10:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>齋口唔齋心</blockquote><br />\n啱，簡直好虛偽"},{"pid":"35b18de2565cbe8ef55def5cf98031bfda8491f3","tid":117062,"uid":357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T16:48:22.000Z","msg":"如果你為左健康食素呢？<br />\n利申支持殺生黎食"},{"pid":"9c533493945000856f59578c139962f9c2ff274f","tid":117062,"uid":357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T16:49:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果係為左健康食素呢？<br />\n利申支持殺生黎食</blockquote>"},{"pid":"fbaf278d1315f1206deab5eadffa637e6a89a07e","tid":117062,"uid":64256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T16:55:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果你為左健康食素呢？<br />\n利申支持殺生黎食</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢啲假肉好唔健康, 大部份油炸, 勁多油, 衰過食快餐, 我自己好少食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0106267d7cde265136ad71b65c42ede8158cbb14","tid":117062,"uid":35233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T16:58:58.000Z","msg":"係咪齋心都好，至少係冇殺生喎"},{"pid":"7232487a358b89b3e221f441e70d99ba70471146","tid":117062,"uid":40632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T17:00:41.000Z","msg":"你鐘意點諗咪點諗 wfc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"271e45138552e7e0983f23846c3a8524a195c295","tid":117062,"uid":18048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T17:02:01.000Z","msg":"素食撚其實可以分兩種<br />\n一種就係樓主講嘅齋口唔齋心嘅素肉（主要用豆整，有啲好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另一種就係純粹嘅食菜瓜果豆穀，調味料都盡量少落<br />\n<br />\n前者戇鳩兼懶係野 <br />\n後者通常低調又唔會周圍叫人同佢一齊食素<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：雜食撚"},{"pid":"0ca62f507bd62a2ba443a514f1386a9e23ed6361","tid":117062,"uid":57337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T17:44:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果你為左健康食素呢？<br />\n利申支持殺生黎食</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢啲假肉好唔健康, 大部份油炸, 勁多油, 衰過食快餐, 我自己好少食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nD假肉咁撚油唔荒健康"},{"pid":"632fffaebab0a81ee22ab050903b5c5e9d1317b6","tid":117062,"uid":61653,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T17:46:49.000Z","msg":"其實有啲人唔係殺生問題而轉食素<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}